{"type": "article", "id": 30075, "title": "巴黎塞纳河边这家酒店，由许多临水的“船舱”组成", "description": "在贴近河面的地方看巴黎是一种仰望的视角，但同时，波光里的巴黎想必有种特别的魅力。", "date": "2016-07-25T05:14:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1124, "name": "巴黎"}, {"id": 9528, "name": "酒店设计"}, {"id": 30586, "name": "OFF hotel"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 147, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607251239599JY1EIg3tCOpzhNV.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>巴黎已经有够多的酒店了，但它也同时意味着对游客的持续吸引力。新开的<a href=\"http://offparisseine.com\" rel=\"nofollow\"> OFF hotel </a>选择了塞纳河的查尔斯戴高乐桥（Charles de Gaulle Bridge）下面，他们请来了一家专做塞纳河畔的事务所&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.ronzatti.com/actualites-en\" rel=\"nofollow\">gèrard ronzatti / seine design</a>&nbsp;设计室内。<br></p><p>酒店由许多临水的“船舱”组成，一共 58 个房间和餐厅、酒吧等公共区域都分布其中。每一个“船舱”的四周是大的落地玻璃窗或可以拉开的门，外面连接着木甲板和一个可以“纵身一跃”的泳池，就像是漂浮在河面上的船。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725124431nabjqTyXcDOKF4i1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>坐在餐厅里，将船身的门打开后，四周就完全敞开了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725124440sjhdrJ3leo9LuBix.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>在走廊中，两个“船舱”之间是一排玻璃天窗，它们向两边微微倾斜呈现出屋顶三角的形状。自然光线通过玻璃窗投射下来，天蓝白云的情景也像是带波光的蓝色湖水。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725124500dxSuPDvshfTwV8EK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725124459HVDoGzNK2vkfR1UA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607251244595men0rTSYMcJWzi1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.674817\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>普通的房间可以选择左右两种窗户朝向， 14 平方米的面积不算大，只放下了一张双人床，电视机和淋浴间。墙面贴着棕色的壁画，室内没有过多的装饰，用木头和锌相间做框架，能给人舒服的感受。窗户和床之间的距离很近，可以直接看到海。</p><p class=\"\">这个房间售价 161 欧元一晚。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016072512453826nJZUmtahxNQF53.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">此外，这家酒店有 4 间套房，一种是具有全局视野的房间，面积扩大至 30 平方米，增加了衣柜和桌椅。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725125439EeMcqhWIxAbuXQHF.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605833\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725124858d8mcSDHvbqNw7ATf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663814\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607251256291LSQ8ABDfX2zyilW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.643032\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">还有一种是设计师房间，比如这间叫“日出”，从墙面到家具以及洗漱间的设施都是橙红色的，让房间处于一种暧昧的情调中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607251251213QTBOWvufGVjME5k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684597\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725125533HZYvfjaI2xszuES4.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725125542twB2VHrCZhnURfWK.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.545000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">另一间叫“银色”，大部分的家具偏灰，黄色的浴缸和洗手池作为调和出现，让这里在柔和明亮中不乏有趣的色彩。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725125620GEjRBhnkgv4qAIs1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645477\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725125731s86BRDxnoEOZkbLp.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.566667\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725125732vKcw0WoVZ2bRhfk6.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.550833\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725125732aLJpmqo78bEis6gP.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.557500\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/off-seine-floating-hotel-paris-gerard-ronzatti-seine-design-07-21-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">designboom</a>、<a href=\"http://offparisseine.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OFF hotel</a><a href=\"http://offparisseine.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">&nbsp;</a></p>"}